                <note rend="inline" type="source">816.51/109: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Salvador</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schuyler</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-11-29T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>39. Your No. 58, November 23, 3 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department believes that matter referred to is not one upon which official
                    opinion should be expressed. If bank requests names of lawyers in San Salvador
                    there is no objection to your suggesting such names.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
